title: Premium Sponsorship
description: Premium service offers a partnership with me where you will significantly contribute to my events. I will promote your business or service by myself. All the posters and banners will reflect your business or service. Most importantly, you will be the highlight of the event.

title: Platinum Sponsorship
description: If you are looking for something special but at a low cost then Platinum Sponsorship will work for you. I will highlight your logo and brand in many ways. Your logo will be attached to my jersey.

title: Golden Sponsorship
description: It is an opportunity to get a simple highlight of my event. This package will hight your logo only and you will not get any special highlights from me. However, it is a great opportunity to promote your brand at a very low cost.

title: Health & Fitness Guide
description: I will guide you to be fit for a professional event so that you can keep on track and increase your chance of winning the race. I will provide you one to one support to develop a healthy and fit body which is required to maintain stamina during heavy work.

title: Tammat's Charity
description: I have a charity program where I provide technical and financial support in rural development. As a single it is a bit hard for me therefore, I need the support of some kind and genuine people. If want to participate feel free to contact me.

title: Learn Cycling
duration: I will guild you to become a professional rider and teach you all the tools and techniques. I will also guide you to be well-prepared for a tournament. It will help you to learn and pursue career at a time.
